-- ds.h3: 🌟 Whats next?
id: what-next

`-- page` component comes with inbuit navbar, sidebar and body content area.
Start creating new `.ftd` files inside your project and use `set-2-ds` `page`
component to write your documentation, blog posts etc.

✨ [Click here](https://fastn-community.github.io/set-2-ds/page/) to know more
details of `page` component.

